## Installation Options

```bash
# Standard install
pip install kstlib

# With uv (faster)
uv pip install kstlib

# Development install
pip install "kstlib[dev]"

# All extras
pip install "kstlib[all]"

# From GitHub (latest)
pip install "git+https://github.com/KaminoU/kstlib.git"
```

